HEADWORD: Snide
<hw>Snide</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Tricky;
deceptive; contemptible; <as>as, a <ex>snide</ex> lawyer; <ex>snide</ex>
goods.</as></def> <mark>[Slang, archaic]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>derogatory in an insinuating manner; <as>as, a
<ex>snide</ex> remark</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

